{
  "id": "terror-squad",
  "name": "Terror Squad",
  "titles": "Terror Squad",
  "lore": "Head hunters, torturers and flayers, within the ranks of the Terror squads were found both the most coldly dispassionate and darkly imaginative of the Night Lords. These warriors were the most unstable and unsubtle elements of the Legion, the midnight and storm clad. Both dark judges and executioners at once, they bore a mixture of weaponry to battle suited to their particular preference. Many also bore the red gauntlets of censure, marked for death by the Night Haunter for their reprehensible actions but allowed to continue their service as long as their grim skills remained of use to the macabre master of the Night Lords.",
